input_str: NOTE: We published the following article a couple of weeks ago, regarding almost 10 minutes of footage that never made it into the final Night of the Living Dead, that was believed to have been lost in a flood. The more we dig into this story, the less we find, and the weaker the sources appear. Nevertheless, we attempted to contact the folks running Monster Mania in Hunt Valley, Maryland, where Romero allegedly dropped this bombshell, and got no response.
